FBIS3-31901 "dreeu039_c_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 CZECH REPUBLIC Havel Supports Peace Initiative in Angola LD2502235394 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network in Czech 2000 GMT 25 Feb 94 LD2502235394 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network Language: Czech Article Type:BFN [Text] President Vaclav Havel today sent a letter to the coordinating committee of the humanitarian campaign "for peace in Angola," with its headquarters in Lisbon. He has thus added his voice to the humanitarian campaign of Africa Amiga, whose aim is to halt the war in Angola. This action, which ends on Sunday, also received support at the beginning of February from Pope John Paul II.
